metadata.name: FIRE N' ICE
metadata.description:
Customized «dare» ambient scent with unique engraving by artist Babybrush.

The engraving's motif is inspired by the song "FIRE N' ICE" - a song from the «I DARE YOU» sessions, which has yet been unreleased.

The collector will exclusively receive the customized ambient scent as a physical object and the song "FIRE N' ICE" as a .WAV file.
